onboarding_survey.messages.1.text: Great! To complete this programme, you'll need a partner in parenting. There are 2 parenting experts to choose from:
Dani is a 35 old mom of 3. She's a clinical psychologist and the first person her friends ask for help with parenting.

Cris is a 38 year old dad. He used to lose his patience and get anxious when spending time with his kids. He worked as a family physician but now coaches parents on the same strategies that helped him.
Who would you like to be your guide?
Hi! I'm @fields.avatar_name! Welcome to @fields.prog_name. You know about me, I would love to know more about you. I will use this information to create a custom programme for you.
